  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to the Operationalization the TRC Lipa</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">As winter approaches, it is imperative to support the Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) in finding immediate solutions to open the new Temporary Reception Centre (TRC) Lipa and ensure the urgent work that was planned is finalized. This intervention therefore contributes to the ongoing humanitarian response in BiH, providing for critical aspects of the functioning of the TRC Lipa what will ensure timely opening and delivery of safe, dignified reception and accommodation services to up to 1,500 migrants and asylum-seekers.</narrative>
  </description>
